  18 Mar 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  libflashsupport-1.2.ebuild:
  Remove USE="esd" because media-soudn/esound isn't in tree anymore.

  03 May 2010; Jim Ramsay <lack@gentoo.org> libflashsupport-1.2.ebuild:
  Removing flash-player block (Bug #300294) and using ewarn instead.

  08 Feb 2010; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> libflashsupport-1.2.ebuild,
  +files/libflashsupport-1.2-gentoo.patch:
  Respect CC, LDFLAGS (bug #268493). Change HOMEPAGE.

  10 Dec 2009; Jim Ramsay <lack@gentoo.org> libflashsupport-1.2.ebuild:
  Block >=www-plugins/adobe-flash-10, this is only needed for flash-9

  05 Dec 2009; Diego E. Petten√≤ <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
